  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 5 June 1924
---
I believe that a healthy soul should inhabit a healthy body. To the extent,
therefore, that the soul grows into health and freedom from passion,
to that extent the body also grows into that state.
